## Comprehensive Database Schema (PostgreSQL)

### 1. Core Users, Access & Profiles
The standard user model is extended to accommodate advanced tiering, fine-grained notification settings, and staff RBAC (Role-Based Access Control).

*   **[User](file:///f:/Webdevelopment/Full%20apps/drop%20ecommerce/drop_ecommerce/src/lib/store.ts#11-22)** (Custom Django Auth Model)
    *   `id` (UUID, Primary Key)
    *   `email` (String, Unique)
    *   `password` (String, Hashed)
    *   `first_name` (String)
    *   `last_name` (String)
    *   `phone_number` (String, Optional)
    *   `role` (Enum: `USER`, `ADMIN_SUPER`, `ADMIN_EDITOR`, `ADMIN_SUPPORT`)
    *   `is_active` (Boolean, Default True)
    *   `date_joined` (DateTime, Auto-Now-Add)

*   **`UserProfile`** (One-to-One linked to [User](file:///f:/Webdevelopment/Full%20apps/drop%20ecommerce/drop_ecommerce/src/lib/store.ts#11-22))
    *   `user` (OneToOneField)
    *   `reward_points` (Integer, Default 0)
    *   `tier_level` (Enum: `BRONZE`, `SILVER`, `GOLD`, Default `BRONZE`)
    *   `order_status_notifications` (Boolean, Default True)
    *   `marketing_notifications` (Boolean, Default False)
    *   `avatar_url` (String/URLField, Nullable)

### 2. User Vault (Addresses & Payments)
*   **`UserAddress`**
    *   `id` (UUID, Primary Key)
    *   `user` (ForeignKey to [User](file:///f:/Webdevelopment/Full%20apps/drop%20ecommerce/drop_ecommerce/src/lib/store.ts#11-22))
    *   `label` (String, e.g., "Home", "Office")
    *   `full_name` (String)
    *   `street_address` (String)
    *   `city` (String)
    *   `state_province` (String)
    *   `postal_code` (String)
    *   `country` (String)
    *   `is_default` (Boolean)

*   **`UserPaymentMethod`** (Tokenized reference, never stores actual card numbers)
    *   `id` (UUID, Primary Key)
    *   `user` (ForeignKey to [User](file:///f:/Webdevelopment/Full%20apps/drop%20ecommerce/drop_ecommerce/src/lib/store.ts#11-22))
    *   `provider_type` (Enum: `VISA`, `MASTERCARD`, `PAYPAL`)
    *   `provider_token` (String, Stripe Customer/PaymentMethod ID)
    *   `last4` (String, Max Length 4, Nullable)
    *   `expiry_month` (Integer, Nullable)
    *   `expiry_year` (Integer, Nullable)
    *   `paypal_email` (String, Nullable)
    *   `is_default` (Boolean)

### 3. Product Catalog & Engagement
Products are complex, supporting variants (size/color) and user wishlists.

*   **`Category`**
    *   `id` (UUID, Primary Key), `name` (String, Unique), `slug` (String, Unique), `parent` (ForeignKey to `Category`, Nullable for nesting)
    
*   **[Product](file:///f:/Webdevelopment/Full%20apps/drop%20ecommerce/drop_ecommerce/src/lib/products.ts#1-12)**
    *   `id` (UUID, Primary Key), `category` (ForeignKey), `title` (String), `slug` (String, Unique)
    *   `description` (Text), `base_price` (Decimal), `stock_quantity` (Integer)
    *   `image_url` (String), `rating_average` (Float, Default 0.0), `rating_count` (Integer, Default 0)
    *   `is_active` (Boolean, Default True)

*   **`ProductVariant`** (Handles specific options like "Size 8" or "Midnight Black")
    *   `id` (UUID, Primary Key)
    *   `product` (ForeignKey to [Product](file:///f:/Webdevelopment/Full%20apps/drop%20ecommerce/drop_ecommerce/src/lib/products.ts#1-12))
    *   `attribute_name` (String, e.g., "Color", "Size")
    *   `attribute_value` (String, e.g., "Red", "10")
    *   `sku_override` (String, Unique, Nullable)
    *   `price_adjustment` (Decimal, Default 0.00)
    *   `stock_quantity` (Integer)

*   **`WishlistItem`**
    *   `user` (ForeignKey to [User](file:///f:/Webdevelopment/Full%20apps/drop%20ecommerce/drop_ecommerce/src/lib/store.ts#11-22)), `product` (ForeignKey to [Product](file:///f:/Webdevelopment/Full%20apps/drop%20ecommerce/drop_ecommerce/src/lib/products.ts#1-12)), `added_at` (DateTime) - *Unique Together constraint on User+Product*

### 4. Cart, Checkout & Orders
Orders retain historic price data, applied discounts, and exact shipping logistics.

*   **[Cart](file:///f:/Webdevelopment/Full%20apps/drop%20ecommerce/drop_ecommerce/src/lib/store.ts#52-97)** & **[CartItem](file:///f:/Webdevelopment/Full%20apps/drop%20ecommerce/drop_ecommerce/src/lib/store.ts#7-10)** (Standard mapping of User/Session to [Product](file:///f:/Webdevelopment/Full%20apps/drop%20ecommerce/drop_ecommerce/src/lib/products.ts#1-12) and/or `ProductVariant` + `quantity`).

*   **[Order](file:///f:/Webdevelopment/Full%20apps/drop%20ecommerce/drop_ecommerce/src/lib/store.ts#23-30)**
    *   `id` (UUID/String prefix like 'FLOW-12345')
    *   `user` (ForeignKey to [User](file:///f:/Webdevelopment/Full%20apps/drop%20ecommerce/drop_ecommerce/src/lib/store.ts#11-22))
    *   `status` (Enum: `PENDING`, `PROCESSING`, `SHIPPED`, `DELIVERED`, `CANCELLED`)
    *   `subtotal` (Decimal)
    *   `tax_amount` (Decimal)
    *   `shipping_fee` (Decimal)
    *   `discount_amount` (Decimal)
    *   `total_amount` (Decimal)
    *   `applied_coupon` (ForeignKey to [Coupon](file:///f:/Webdevelopment/Full%20apps/drop%20ecommerce/drop_ecommerce/src/app/admin/coupons/page.tsx#63-270), Nullable)
    *   `shipping_address` (JSONField - Snapshot of address at time of order)
    *   `billing_address` (JSONField - Snapshot)
    *   `payment_status` (String: `PAID`, `FAILED`, `PENDING`)
    *   `created_at` (DateTime), `updated_at` (DateTime)

*   **`OrderItem`**
    *   `order` (ForeignKey), `product` (ForeignKey), `variant` (ForeignKey, Nullable)
    *   `quantity` (Integer), `unit_price_at_purchase` (Decimal)

### 5. Promotional Engine & Global Store Configurations
Supports the complex admin dashboard for coupons and store settings.

*   **[Coupon](file:///f:/Webdevelopment/Full%20apps/drop%20ecommerce/drop_ecommerce/src/app/admin/coupons/page.tsx#63-270)**
    *   `id` (UUID, Primary Key), `code` (String, Unique, Uppercase)
    *   `discount_type` (Enum: `PERCENTAGE`, `FIXED_AMOUNT`, `FREE_SHIPPING`)
    *   `discount_value` (Decimal)
    *   `usage_limit` (Integer, Nullable), `current_usage` (Integer, Default 0)
    *   `min_order_value` (Decimal, Default 0.00)
    *   `valid_from` (DateTime), `expires_at` (DateTime, Nullable)
    *   `is_active` (Boolean, Default True)

*   **`StoreConfiguration`** (Singleton Table - Only 1 row ever exists)
    *   `store_name`, `contact_email`, `currency_code` (e.g. 'USD'), `time_zone`
    *   `measurement_system` (Enum: `METRIC`, `IMPERIAL`)
    *   `maintenance_mode` (Boolean, Default False), `robots_indexing` (Boolean, Default True)
    *   `auto_vat_calculation` (Boolean)

*   **`ShippingZone`**
    *   `id` (UUID), `region_name` (String), `included_countries` (ArrayField/Text), `flat_rate` (Decimal, Nullable - If null, calculated dynamically)

