## Detailed API Endpoints (DRF)

### Public & Authentication (`/api/v1/`)
*   `POST /auth/register/` - Create User & UserProfile.
*   `POST /auth/login/` - Returns JWT Access/Refresh tokens.
*   `GET/PATCH /account/profile/` - Manage personal info, reward tiers, and notification flags.
*   `GET/POST/DELETE /account/addresses/` - CRUD for `UserAddress` (Handle `is_default` toggles).
*   `GET/POST/DELETE /account/payments/` - Manage `UserPaymentMethod` token references.
*   `GET/POST/DELETE /account/wishlist/` - Manage liked products.

### Commerce Engine (`/api/v1/`)
*   `GET /products/` - List products. Queries: `?category=slug&sort=price&in_stock=true`.
*   `GET /products/{slug}/` - Includes nested array of `ProductVariant` options.
*   `GET /categories/` - Returns nested tree structure of categories.
*   `POST /cart/sync/` - Syncs localstorage guest cart with DB on login.
*   `GET/POST/PUT/DELETE /cart/items/` - Standard cart management.
*   `POST /checkout/validate-coupon/` - Checks coupon logic against cart total.
*   `POST /checkout/process/` - Converts Cart to Order, charges Payment Gateway, adjusts Stock, and awards User Reward Points.

### Admin Dashboard API (`/api/v1/admin/`) - *Requires `role != USER`*
*   **Analytics**: `GET /analytics/overview/` - Returns revenue, order counts, new customers for graphs.
*   **Coupons**: `GET/POST/PUT/DELETE /coupons/` - Full CRUD for the promotional engine.
*   **Orders**: `GET /orders/` (List all), `PATCH /orders/{id}/status/` (Update picking/shipping status).
*   **Catalog**: `POST/PUT /products/`, `POST/PUT /categories/` - Manage inventory and variants.
*   **Settings**: `GET/PATCH /settings/global/` - Update `StoreConfiguration`.
*   **Shipping**: `GET/POST/PUT /settings/shipping-zones/`.
*   **Staff**: `GET/POST /staff/` - Invite/manage admin staff (Requires `ADMIN_SUPER`).

